<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Vostok Dynamics</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Russo+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #ffffff;
    font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6vh 6vw;
  }

  .hero img {
    max-width: 55vw;
    max-height: 55vh;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .date {
    font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    color: #d92b2b;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .quote-block {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .quote {
    font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.4rem);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .attribution {
    font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.8vw, 1.1rem);
    color: #c9a400;
  }

  /* extra scrollable space below the hero */
  .spacer {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <section class="hero">
    <img src="VOSTOK_DYNAMICS.png" alt="Vostok Dynamics">

    <h1 class="date">April 12, 1961</h1>

    <div class="quote-block">
      <p class="quote">"To be the first to enter the cosmos, to engage, single-handed, in an unprecedented duel with nature—could one dream of anything more?"</p>
      <p class="attribution">— Yuri Gagarin</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="spacer"></section>

</body>
</html>
